- - - - Clean Clean false false false EN-US X-NONE X-NONE MicrosoftInternetExplorer4 Hi Jim, I just had a chance to speak with Kim and I wanted to send you some additional information on the “MBO Exec” program for you to review via email since you are currently traveling and not able to connect via phone. - To review information not published on our website about the MBO Program you may go to my Landing Page by clicking here. <http://info.mbopartners.com/advisor-info-s-conde.html> - Additional links about Financial Benefits of working with MBO as well as MBO Testimonials - http://info.mbopartners.com/rs/mbo/images/MBO_Exec_Financial_Advantages.pdf <http://info.mbopartners.com/rs/mbo/images/MBO_Exec_Financial_Advantages.pdf> - http://info.mbopartners.com/rs/mbo/images/MBO_Partners_Testimonials.pdf <http://info.mbopartners.com/rs/mbo/images/MBO_Partners_Testimonials.pdf>
In addition to that information, our fee is 5.0% of the first $125,000 of cash receipts from Clients for services beginning on Effective Date and each anniversary thereafter. 1.5% after the first $125,000 of cash receipts from Clients with the Standard Associate Fee Plan until the anniversary of Effective Date. If you would like to hear more about our services, feel free to schedule a convenient time for you using my online calendar. <https://my.timedriver.com/8SLYS> I look forward to speaking with you!
